[32m│[0m ## RECONNAISSANCE SUMMARY                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### ANALYSIS                                                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The task requires exploiting an AES-CBC encrypted cookie without MAC         [32m│[0m
