[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### DISCOVERED INFORMATION                                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m #### **Endpoints:**                                                          [32m│[0m
