[32m│[0m password                                                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **/welcome** (GET) - Protected page displaying "Welcome, <username>!"      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **/static/style.css** - Static resources                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Non-existent: /logout, /admin, /dashboard, /robots.txt, /.git/config       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m #### **Valid Credentials:**                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Username: `test1`                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Password: `test1`                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Source: HTML comment in login page (`<!-- test1:test1 TODO: remove-->`)    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m #### **Authentication Flow:**                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. POST to `/login` with form data: `username=test1&password=test1`          [32m│[0m
