[32m│[0m 5. Accessing `/welcome` without valid cookie redirects to `/` (login page)   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m #### **Session Cookie Structure:**                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Cookie name:** `session`                                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Format:** 64 hexadecimal characters (32 bytes when decoded)              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Encoding:** Hex-encoded ciphertext                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Example:**                                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m `56c8488525dfccf5972183000303974c30ea51aeef2f5abed035956d18027478`           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m #### **Encryption Characteristics:**                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Non-deterministic:** Same username produces different cookies each login [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m (uses random IV/nonce)                                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Fixed length:** Cookie is always 64 hex chars (32 bytes) regardless of   [32m│[0m
