[32m│[0m - **Malleable:** Modifying individual ciphertext bytes directly affects      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m corresponding plaintext bytes                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **No integrity protection:** No HMAC or cryptographic signature to detect  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m tampering                                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m #### **Vulnerability Confirmed:**                                            [32m│[0m
