[32m│[0m    - Position 2: 's'(0x73) XOR 'm'(0x6d) = 0x1e                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m    - Position 3: 't'(0x74) XOR 'i'(0x69) = 0x1d                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m    - Position 4: '1'(0x31) XOR 'n'(0x6e) = 0x5f                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. Apply XOR transformation to first 5 bytes of the cookie hex string        [32m│[0m
